description: Gusto Criollo operates out of the Fort Sam Houston Military Installation cooking the most authentic Puerto Rican Cuisine in San Antonio. Open from 11:00- 2:00 PM and selected Friday evenings for dinner. Enjoy a variety of popular and traditional Boricua Cuisine from Monday thru Friday. Menu changes to give our customers a different Puerto Rican experience every day! We are located across the street from Popeye’s Chicken in the parking lot by the Class Six store. Enter Walters Gate, continue straight pass the first traffic light and we will be on your right.Buen Provecho!
name: Gusto Criollo
